subject: United States Open (Tennis)
Tennis
lead_paragraph: Second-seeded Rafael Nadal struggled with knee trouble and an unheralded first-round opponent before defeating 123rd-ranked Alun Jones, 7-5, 3-6, 6-4, 6-1.
